<div class="community-section">
<div class="community-section-heading"><span>IRC Live Chat</span></div>
<div class="community-section-text">

The core of the community is currently on <a
href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Internet_Relay_Chat">IRC</a>. Join <a
href="irc://irc.freenode.net/esp" title="Join #esp IRC Chat">#esp</a> on
<code>irc.freenode.net</code>. You can use <a
href="http://webchat.freenode.net/?channels=esp" title="Join #esp IRC Chat">this
webchat client</a> as well as browse the live <a href="http://irclogs.ampify.it"
title="See #esp IRC logs">chatlogs</a>.

</div>
</div>

<div class="community-section">
<div class="community-section-heading"><span>Mailing Lists</span></div>
<div class="community-section-text">

You can engage others at <code>ampify@googlegroups.com</code>, the official <a
href="http://groups.google.com/group/ampify">ampify mailing list</a>. Developers
should use the <a
href="http://groups.google.com/group/ampify-dev">ampify-dev</a> list. You can
also email <a href="mailto:help@ampify.it">help@ampify.it</a>.

</div>
</div>

<div class="community-section">
<div class="community-section-heading"><span>Twitter</span></div>
<div class="community-section-text">

Use the <a href="http://twitter.com/search?q=%23ampify"
title="#ampify">#ampify</a> hashtag to join the <a
href="http://search.twitter.com/search?q=%23ampify+OR+%23espians+OR+%23trustmap+OR+from%3Aespians+OR+to%3Aespians+OR+from%3Aampify+OR+to%3Aampify"
title="See the conversation on Twitter">conversation on Twitter</a>. Likewise,
you can post your thoughts/links to the <a href="http://friendfeed.com/espians"
title="Join the Espians FriendFeed room">Espians room</a> on FriendFeed.

</div>
</div>

<div class="community-banner">
<span class="community-banner-text">
Thank you and welcome to Espia!
</span>
